msgstr "akonadiclient import [ПАРАМЕТРИ] БАТЬКІВСЬКА_ЗБІРКА ФАЙЛ"

#. Tag: para
#: man-akonadiclient.1.docbook:346
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Imports an XML file inside the collection specified by PARENT. If the "
"collection already exists, its contents are merged with the contents of the "
